<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>com.timenzo.Tracker</id>
  
  <name>Timenzo</name>
  <summary>Time tracking with activity monitoring for Odoo</summary>
  
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>Proprietary</project_license>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Timenzo is a comprehensive time tracking application designed for Odoo 18 Enterprise
      that monitors your productivity across all applications.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Automatic time tracking with project and task management</li>
      <li>Multi-monitor screenshot capture with configurable intervals</li>
      <li>Real-time activity monitoring (keystrokes, mouse clicks, movement)</li>
      <li>Idle detection and auto-pause functionality</li>
      <li>App categorization (productive, neutral, distracting)</li>
      <li>Dark/light theme support</li>
      <li>Offline queue with automatic sync</li>
      <li>Native Linux support (X11 and Wayland)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Note: Requires Odoo 18 Enterprise with the desktop_time_tracking module installed.
      This is a client application that connects to your Odoo instance.
    </p>
  </description>
  
